   Program Summary: Program Direction

   Vision Statement
   Replacement of methyl bromide by January 1, 2005, with effective,
   economical and practical alternatives

   Mission Statement
   To develop environmentally compatible and economically feasible
   alternatives to the use of methyl bromide as a soil and postharvest
   commodity treatment.

   Program Components
     * Preplant Soil Fumigation Alternatives
     * Postharvest Commodity Treatment (Including Structural)


